The '''Stattkus-Verzeichnis''' ('''SV''') is a catalogue of the musical compositions of the Italian composer [[Claudio Monteverdi]]. The catalogue was published in 1985 by Manfred H. Stattkus (''Claudio Monteverdi: Verzeichnis der erhaltenen Werke''). A free, basic second edition of the catalogue is available online.<ref>''[http://www.dieter-ewerth.de/Stattkus-Musik/Basic-1.pdf Monteverdi-Catalog "Verzeichnis der erhaltenen Werke"]''. 2007-05-12.(changed 2012-09-25)</ref>
Manfred H. Stattkus died in August 2012.
